  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/dbc22872f4532232f41a49cb67cb3d3f.poster.avif?t=1724965097\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/dbc22872f4532232f41a49cb67cb3d3f.webm?t=1724965097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/dbc22872f4532232f41a49cb67cb3d3f.mp4?t=1724965097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Time to Strike mixes Binding of Issac crazy synergies with more streamlined gameplay with a gentle sprinkle of Vampire Survivors. Runs are fast and items are made to synergize with each other!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/d4211ae56d7538e4901576dd0a4007c5.poster.avif?t=1724965097\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/d4211ae56d7538e4901576dd0a4007c5.webm?t=1724965097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/d4211ae56d7538e4901576dd0a4007c5.mp4?t=1724965097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>There are tons of build options to experiment with. Become summon master, create critter army, demolish enemies with massive explosions, fill screen with bullets or anything in between, it is up to you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/8a7e52b21b051b0c6117ae0fd6324239.poster.avif?t=1724965097\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/8a7e52b21b051b0c6117ae0fd6324239.webm?t=1724965097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/8a7e52b21b051b0c6117ae0fd6324239.mp4?t=1724965097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast runs<br></li><li>30+ unique weapons<br></li><li>30+ powerful mods to modify your weapons<br></li><li>80+ fun relics to experiment with<br></li><li>Tons of starting options to play around<br></li><li>5 boss fights</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/dbc22872f4532232f41a49cb67cb3d3f.poster.avif?t=1724965097\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/dbc22872f4532232f41a49cb67cb3d3f.webm?t=1724965097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/dbc22872f4532232f41a49cb67cb3d3f.mp4?t=1724965097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Time to Strike mixes Binding of Issac crazy synergies with more streamlined gameplay with a gentle sprinkle of Vampire Survivors. Runs are fast and items are made to synergize with each other!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/d4211ae56d7538e4901576dd0a4007c5.poster.avif?t=1724965097\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/d4211ae56d7538e4901576dd0a4007c5.webm?t=1724965097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/d4211ae56d7538e4901576dd0a4007c5.mp4?t=1724965097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>There are tons of build options to experiment with. Become summon master, create critter army, demolish enemies with massive explosions, fill screen with bullets or anything in between, it is up to you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603410/extras/8a7e52b21b051b0c6117ae0fd6324239.poster.avif?t=1724965097\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com